ent-CCMWeaponLMGTovarish = Tovarish Petrishev
    .desc = An unique piece of underground terrorism armory. Chambered in 7.62x54mmR, this Frankenstein is, unlike any NORMAL LMG, designed for a direct frontline combat. Despite being an abomination of a handmade forge factory, it can deliver death as effective as any other machine gun.
